Web Based Active Directory Management with ManageEngine ADManager Plus
Download ADManager Plus Download
Install ADManager Plus, skipping the registration step
Once the installation completes, open a web browser and navigate to http://DNSorIP:8080
Login with username admin and password admin
Click the Click here to add a new domain link
Complete the form, enabling the Authentication checkbox and entering the Domain Name, Username and Password
Click the Discover New link
Type the domain controller host name(s) > Click Add
Click Add to complete setting up the domain
Welcome to web based Active Directory administration with ADManager Plus
